data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-story home bursting with potential! Step inside and be greeted by the timeless beauty of this residence. The main floor offers two bedrooms, a cozy living room featuring a fireplace and hardwood floors, a welcoming dining room, and a kitchen adorned with updated appliances and laminate floor.  Upstairs, you'll find a spacious, full-length room with closets, versatile enough to serve as a bedroom, office, or playroom – let your imagination run wild! The full basement provides ample storage space, a dedicated work area, and houses the water heater.  Enjoy your morning coffee on the covered front porch while admiring the perennial flowers that grace the front yard, including mock orange, hydrangeas, honeysuckle, and several peonies. The backyard is equally charming, featuring a mature apple tree, cedars, and a walnut tree. Plus, the garden shed is included for all your outdoor storage needs.
